WEBVTT

00:04:25.912 --> 00:04:30.809
or maybe you don't hear it because people are too polite to say it, is,

00:04:30.809 --> 00:04:35.272
why should I pay more taxes

00:04:35.272 --> 00:04:39.550
to invest in other people's children?

00:04:39.550 --> 00:04:42.044
What's in it for me?

00:04:42.044 --> 00:04:44.323
